body_html:
@harpone: pip install tf-nightly should do it!

But as you observed in EDIT2, the code in Dataset.from_generator() is built entirely out of transformations that were available in TF 1.3, so you can copy its implementation into your project and use it directly.

body:
@harpone: `pip install tf-nightly` should do it!

But as you observed in EDIT2, the code in `Dataset.from_generator()` is built entirely out of transformations that were available in TF 1.3, so you can copy its implementation into your project and use it directly.
